t method, such as, YourInterface getIntance(). you should extend this abstr=
act class for each class&#39;s testcase implemented the interface, the only thi=
ng you should do in the subclass implementing the getInstance method, in th=
is method you should return an instance of the concrete class.
=20
for example:
=20
